# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:179
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_91f732d4:

#   l "Hey [p_name_short], you’re looking well."
    l "Hola [p_name_short], tienes buen aspecto."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:180
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_669912bb:

#   c "I’m feeling a little better."
    c "Me siento un poco mejor."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:182
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_24818aa2:

#   l "Happy to hear that."
    l "Me alegra oírlo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:183
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_0e93075b:

#   c "Do you have a moment for me?"
    c "¿Tienes un momento para mí?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:184
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_a114f3f8:

#   l "Of course."
    l "Por supuesto."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:185
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_964bfe12:

#   c "Have you kept up with the news reports from the Sovereignty?"
    c "¿Has seguido las noticias de la Soberanía?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:187
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_e1c95b98:

#   l "Yes, I was about to message you about that."
    l "Sí, estaba a punto de enviarte un mensaje sobre eso."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:188
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_6e581b9c:

#   l "I’ve scraped together what I could find."
    l "He reunido lo que he podido encontrar."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:189
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_bcdf24db:

#   c "Anything recent?"
    c "¿Algo reciente?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:190
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_0e437111:

#   c "About Agust, I mean?"
    c "¿Sobre Agust, quiero decir?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:192
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_507dd7b2:

#   l "Oh yes and you’re not going to like it."
    l "Ah, sí, y no te va a gustar."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:194
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_19c32bb6:

#   c "Nothing about Dad is ever good news, so hit me."
    c "Nada sobre papá son buenas noticias, así que pégame."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:196
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_b4567d78:

#   c "Nothing about my father is ever good news, so hit me."
    c "Nada sobre mi padre son buenas noticias, así que pégame."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:198
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_968aa29f:

#   l "Remember those terrorist attacks?"
    l "¿Recuerdas los atentados terroristas?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:199
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_822ac5fd:

#   c "Carried out by that group, the Auric Exemplar?"
    c "¿Llevado a cabo por ese grupo, el Auric Exemplar?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:201
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_ddf50bb8:

#   l "Exactly."
    l "Exactamente."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:202
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_7ab3e039:

#   l "Their terror campaign has continued pretty much unabatedly."
    l "Su campaña de terror ha continuado prácticamente sin interrupción."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:203
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_ef07bc6d:

#   c "Nothing new there, then."
    c "Nada nuevo, pues."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:204
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_bda440cc:

#   l "No, not until a few weeks ago."
    l "No, no hasta hace unas semanas."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:206
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_057ecc94:

#   l "Dad’s return wasn’t mentioned in any news feeds I could find."
    l "El regreso de papá no se mencionó en ninguna noticia que pude encontrar."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:208
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_c43de77d:

#   l "Agust’s return wasn’t mentioned in any news feeds I could find."
    l "El regreso de Agust no se mencionó en ninguna de las noticias que pude encontrar."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:209
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_9994ddd6:

#   l "Not even the TGN Ypotryll was reported back."
    l "Ni siquiera el TGN Ypotryll fue reportado."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:210
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_0a583fd9:

#   c "He needed medical treatment after the procedure on Petrarch, didn’t he?"
    c "Necesitó tratamiento médico después del procedimiento en Petrarca, ¿no?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:211
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_eaa6292b:

#   c "So maybe he got treated for that heart attack in some clandestine facility."
    c "Así que tal vez fue tratado por ese ataque al corazón en alguna instalación clandestina."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:213
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_43ed8f16:

#   l "Maybe."
    l "Tal vez."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:214
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_506afec7:

#   l "The fact is, for the past few weeks his name is suddenly mentioned again."
    l "El caso es que desde hace unas semanas su nombre vuelve a mencionarse de repente."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:215
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_543f4480:

#   l "Like he popped up suddenly."
    l "Como si hubiera aparecido de repente."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:216
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_e7d9561d:

#   c "Like the cockroach that he is."
    c "Como la cucaracha que es."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:217
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_cfe6f443:

#   c "So he got a mention in the business section of some provincial newspaper?"
    c "¿Así que consiguió una mención en la sección de negocios de algún periódico provincial?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:218
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_43e4d03b:

#   c "“Local businessman returns home, is still an insufferable cunt”, something like that?"
    c "\"Empresario local vuelve a casa, sigue siendo un cabrón insufrible\", ¿algo así?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:220
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_4241539e:

#   l "No, this is something major."
    l "No, esto es algo importante."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:221
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_83ad2999:

#   l "There have been assassination attempts on members of the Sovereignty Council before."
    l "Ya ha habido intentos de asesinato de miembros del Consejo de Soberanía."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:222
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_8e40b069:

#   l "Some were successful, others were thwarted."
    l "Algunos tuvieron éxito, otros se vieron frustrados."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:223
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_1e57b8f9:

#   l "This time, when the Council was officially in session, they were wiped out by someone or something."
    l "Esta vez, cuando el Consejo estaba oficialmente reunido, fueron aniquilados por alguien o algo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:224
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_364b6f7d:

#   c "But not all of them..."
    c "Pero no todos..."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:226
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_0fab2e42:

#   l "No, Dad survived somehow."
    l "No, papá sobrevivió de alguna manera."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:228
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_c36f3cdb:

#   l "No, Agust survived somehow."
    l "No, Agust sobrevivió de alguna manera."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:229
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_4c633a45:

#   l "He was the only one."
    l "Era el único."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:230
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_68d3aa61:

#   l "But if there are any other survivors, nothing was reported about them escaping."
    l "Pero si hay otros supervivientes, no se ha informado de que hayan escapado."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:231
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_60ba8799:

#   c "What happened exactly?"
    c "¿Qué ha pasado exactamente?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:232
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_fd8a48b4:

#   l "Several explosions were reported, as well as a couple of power surges."
    l "Se registraron varias explosiones, así como un par de subidas de tensión."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:233
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_710277d4:

#   l "No tactical strike teams were spotted beforehand, nor any orbital assault."
    l "No se avistaron equipos de ataque táctico de antemano, ni ningún asalto orbital."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:234
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_b0ae2781:

#   l "Nobody knows what caused all that, but a state of emergency has been declared until further notice."
    l "Nadie sabe qué causó todo aquello, pero se ha declarado el estado de emergencia hasta nuevo aviso."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:235
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_8d34f3be:

#   c "I think I have a pretty clear idea about who is responsible for those surges and explosions."
    c "Creo que tengo una idea bastante clara sobre quién es el responsable de esas oleadas y explosiones."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:238
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_e9354ca6:

#   l "Yes, Dad is involved somehow, isn’t he?"
    l "Sí, papá está involucrado de alguna manera, ¿no?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:240
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_0e9c3796:

#   l "Yes, Agust is involved somehow, isn’t he?"
    l "Sí, Agust está involucrado de alguna manera, ¿no?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:241
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_50b90fc2:

#   c "He sure is."
    c "Claro que sí."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:242
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_1c356b9f:

#   c "I would go as far to say that he is directly responsible."
    c "Me atrevería a decir que es directamente responsable."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:243
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_7b6b0099:

#   c "Him and his new-found powers."
    c "Él y sus nuevos poderes."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:244
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_9d06a1f3:

#   l "You mean he murdered the Council?"
    l "¿Quieres decir que asesinó al Consejo?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:245
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_31a9e8a5:

#   c "An indefinite state of emergency has been declared, right?"
    c "Se ha declarado un estado de emergencia indefinido, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:246
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_cd115d85:

#   c "And who’s the new single ruler, controlling everything from the Department of Interplanetary Exploration to the Navy now that the Council has conveniently died out?"
    c "¿Y quién es el nuevo gobernante único, que controla todo, desde el Departamento de Exploración Interplanetaria hasta la Marina, ahora que el Consejo se ha extinguido convenientemente?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:249
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_0de97101:

#   l "Dad is..."
    l "Papá es..."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:251
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_380dc5c3:

#   l "Agust is..."
    l "Agust es..."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:252
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_f9c698b6:

#   c "Exactly."
    c "Exactamente."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:253
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_b0567354:

#   c "He was the one who announced the state of emergency, wasn’t he?"
    c "Fue él quien anunció el estado de emergencia, ¿no?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:254
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_bc5c265b:

#   l "Yes."
    l "Sí."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:255
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_0366f5cd:

#   c "You said that nobody knows what caused the slaughter of the Council."
    c "Dijiste que nadie sabe qué causó la matanza del Consejo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:256
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_ee80afa4:

#   l "That’s right."
    l "Así es."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:257
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_aa51f567:

#   l "There’s a press conference today about it."
    l "Hoy hay una rueda de prensa al respecto."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:258
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_e6de724f:

#   l "In fact, it has already started."
    l "De hecho, ya ha comenzado."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:260
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_6b5587f5:

#   c "Could you pull up that feed?"
    c "¿Podrías subir esa información?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:261
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_705a04b2:

#   l "Sure."
    l "Sí, claro."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:263
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_b8ea7b92:

#   ag "...dark times."
    ag "...tiempos oscuros."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:264
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_ce56c559:

#   ag "The enemy has struck a terrible blow, right in the heart of our beloved Sovereignty."
    ag "El enemigo ha asestado un golpe terrible, justo en el corazón de nuestra amada Soberanía."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:265
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_61245719:

#   ag "The Council is no more, murdered in cold blood."
    ag "El Consejo ya no existe, asesinado a sangre fría."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:267
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_79605fb3:

#   ag "I was able to escape the slaughter and was rescued by the brave men and women of our armed forces."
    ag "Pude escapar de la matanza y fui rescatado por los valientes hombres y mujeres de nuestras fuerzas armadas."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:268
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_a42ccf26:

#   ag "As proclaimed earlier, the state of emergency will continue until the investigation into this grave matter has been concluded and the culprits have been found and executed for their heinous crimes."
    ag "Como se ha proclamado anteriormente, el estado de emergencia continuará hasta que concluya la investigación de este grave asunto y se encuentre y ejecute a los culpables de sus atroces crímenes."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:269
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_59ad64cd:

#   ag "The investigation team is still working hard on their findings, but I can already divulge that the attack was likely carried out by enemy agents."
    ag "El equipo de investigación todavía está trabajando duro en sus conclusiones, pero ya puedo divulgar que el ataque fue probablemente llevado a cabo por agentes enemigos."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:270
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_43bdf796:

#   ag "Enemy agents who received help from traitors inside the Sovereignty."
    ag "Agentes enemigos que recibieron ayuda de traidores dentro de la Soberanía."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:272
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_126d3194:

#   ag "Traitors like the Auric Exemplar."
    ag "Traidores como el Auric Exemplar."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:273
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_39bb1b77:

#   ag "As Regent, I will make sure that the cowardly attackers will be prosecuted to the fullest extent of the law."
    ag "Como Regente, me aseguraré de que los cobardes atacantes sean procesados con todo el peso de la ley."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:274
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_7aae6468:

#   ag "I will shepherd our Sovereignty to newfound heights of greatness."
    ag "Guiaré a nuestra Soberanía a nuevas cotas de grandeza."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:275
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_92495420:

#   ag "The Sovereignty will never bow to terror, and so I’ve asked the Terran Galatic Navy to carry out a series of punitive actions against those territories that have a history of being outright hostile and disloyal to our great nation."
    ag "La Soberanía nunca se doblegará ante el terror, por lo que he pedido a la Armada Galaica Terran que lleve a cabo una serie de acciones punitivas contra aquellos territorios que tengan un historial de franca hostilidad y deslealtad hacia nuestra gran nación."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:276
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_c2a8e261:

#   ag "Orbital bombardments are carried out in the Dra-Hynyn and Ovalt Vhil systems at this time."
    ag "En estos momentos se llevan a cabo bombardeos orbitales en los sistemas Dra-Hynyn y Ovalt Vhil."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:277
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_658f5e10:

#   ag "We will not hesitate to put into position the full military might of the Sovereignty against anyone who dares to oppose us."
    ag "No dudaremos en poner en posición todo el poderío militar de la Soberanía contra cualquiera que ose oponerse a nosotros."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:278
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_07012cfd:

#   ag "The Sovereignty will prevail!"
    ag "¡La Soberanía prevalecerá!"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:279
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_cc0ff136:

#   ag "Long live the Sovereignty!"
    ag "¡Viva la Soberanía!"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:280
translate spanish ep023_lilly_talk_eba7a1ec:

#   c "I think I’ve heard enough."
    c "Creo que ya he oído bastante."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:282
