translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_46e7ae80:

#   na "The Council was already weakened by the murders they pinned on the Auric Exemplar."
    na "El Consejo ya estaba debilitado por los asesinatos que atribuían al Ejemplar Áurico."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:733
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_a2f18e4e:

#   na "What’s the official story put out by the Sovereignty about the massacre?"
    na "¿Cuál es la historia oficial publicada por el Soberano sobre la masacre?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:734
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_f1d3e813:

#   c "They’re pinning it on domestic terrorism, mentioning the Auric Exemplar directly and outside influences."
    c "Lo achacan al terrorismo interno, mencionan directamente al Auric Exemplar e influencias externas."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:735
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_932fc1e4:

#   na "Outside influences as in other species interfering with the Sovereignty?"
    na "¿Influencias externas como en otras especies que interfieren con la Soberanía?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:736
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_910cb064:

#   c "Yes, they seem to be gearing up for an all out war, with Agust as some kind of war leader."
    c "Sí, parece que se están preparando para una guerra total, con Agust como una especie de líder de guerra."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:738
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_a4b10f6b:

#   na "That makes sense."
    na "Eso tiene sentido."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:739
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_18ac2ef8:

#   na "Agust must be very confident in the abilities he gained on Petrarch to make a power-play like this."
    na "Agust debe tener mucha confianza en las habilidades que adquirió en Petrarca para hacer una jugada de poder como esta."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:740
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_31d1e5e8:

#   c "Yes, and the power-grab seems to have succeeded, so he must have the backing of other powerful people as well."
    c "Sí, y la toma de poder parece haber tenido éxito, por lo que debe tener el respaldo de otras personas poderosas también."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:742
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_67069e37:

#   na "If Agust has the power to singlehandedly destroy the Council, would you be able to do the same?"
    na "Si Agust tiene el poder de destruir sin ayuda al Consejo, ¿serías capaz de hacer lo mismo?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:743
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_cf2a6a99:

#   c "I guess so."
    c "Supongo que sí."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:744
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_695c134b:

#   c "Agust and I were exposed to the procedure for the same amount of time."
    c "Agust y yo estuvimos expuestos al procedimiento durante el mismo tiempo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:745
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_79d42f31:

#   c "Considering what I did to Eva, I reckon the process could be reversed."
    c "Considerando lo que le hice a Eva, creo que el proceso podría invertirse."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:746
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_964211a4:

#   c "In fact, it might be as simple as stopping someone’s heart."
    c "De hecho, podría ser tan sencillo como detener el corazón de alguien."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:747
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_3818d9a3:

#   na "Simple..."
    na "Simple..."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:748
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_eeea05b3:

#   c "Simple compared to breathing life into someone again."
    c "Sencillo comparado con insuflar vida a alguien de nuevo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:750
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_e2288957:

#   na "Damn, that’s a terrible thing to contemplate."
    na "Maldita sea, es algo terrible de contemplar."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:751
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_4d62908b:

#   c "What I don’t get is his desire to wage war and to subjugate new systems."
    c "Lo que no entiendo es su deseo de hacer la guerra y subyugar nuevos sistemas."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:752
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_7596399c:

#   c "I mean, he’s already Regent of a mind-boggling territory, why the need for expansion?"
    c "Ya es Regente de un territorio alucinante, ¿por qué la necesidad de expansión?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:754
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_aaca0977:

#   na "Your father wants to create a legacy."
    na "Tu padre quiere crear un legado."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:755
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_f55d0ad0:

#   na "To be a major figure in the history books."
    na "Ser una figura importante en los libros de historia."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:756
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_944dc427:

#   na "It’s what every power-hungry tyrant desires."
    na "Es lo que todo tirano sediento de poder desea."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:757
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_f7eed2bf:

#   na "Right now, he’s busy to consolidate his power base."
    na "Ahora mismo, está ocupado en consolidar su base de poder."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:758
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_e176b148:

#   na "Because eventually people will start to ask questions about what happened exactly to the Council and having absolute power over the judiciary and government would be very beneficial in that case."
    na "Porque al final la gente empezará a hacerse preguntas sobre qué pasó exactamente con el Consejo y tener poder absoluto sobre el poder judicial y el gobierno sería muy beneficioso en ese caso."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:759
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_db570863:

#   c "As is the distraction of waging an interplanetary war."
    c "Al igual que la distracción de librar una guerra interplanetaria."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:760
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_f2ad077b:

#   na "Exactly."
    na "Exactamente."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:761
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_a3a2b6b0:

#   na "Your father already was a dangerous man when he was still rising through the ranks."
    na "Tu padre ya era un hombre peligroso cuando aún ascendía en el escalafón."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:763
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_4920e85c:

#   na "With the competition of the Confessor and the Council eliminated, I don’t think anybody will stand in his way."
    na "Eliminada la competencia de la Confesora y el Consejo, no creo que nadie se interponga en su camino."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:764
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_397ef7cd:

#   c "That’s what I thought as well."
    c "Eso es lo que yo pensaba también."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:765
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_3a6ebaba:

#   c "Could you meet me later in my quarters?"
    c "¿Podrías reunirte conmigo más tarde en mis aposentos?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:766
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_dd43dc53:

#   c "Eva, Lilly and Aven are also invited."
    c "Eva, Lilly y Aven también están invitados."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:767
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_c6af356b:

#   na "Yes, of course."
    na "Sí, por supuesto."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:769
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_68b556e7:

#   na "But why do you want us all together?"
    na "¿Pero por qué nos quieres a todos juntos?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:771
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_111f502e:

#   c "I want revenge, Mom."
    c "Quiero vengarme, mamá."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:773
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_813acb73:

#   c "I want revenge, Nadya."
    c "Quiero venganza, Nadya."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:774
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_4c4f7448:

#   c "And I think I have a plan on how to achieve that."
    c "Y creo que tengo un plan para conseguirlo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:776
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_afb96bfe:

#   na "[p_name], you are talking about the newly crowned Regent of the Sovereignty."
    na "[p_name], estás hablando del recién coronado Regente de la Soberanía."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:777
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_306623f8:

#   na "He’s likely protected by several layers of security and there are his powers to consider."
    na "Probablemente esté protegido por varias capas de seguridad y hay que tener en cuenta sus poderes."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:778
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_fe8f2fec:

#   c "I know, but please hear me out first."
    c "Lo sé, pero por favor, escúchame primero."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:780
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_930d0cfe:

#   na "Okay, I guess I’ll see you later in your quarters."
    na "Vale, supongo que te veré más tarde en tus aposentos."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:784
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_474eaa7e:

#   na "Or, if you’re not busy, you could stay the night."
    na "O, si no estás ocupado, puedes quedarte a pasar la noche."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:785
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_56a3ab78:

#   c "I’d like that very much."
    c "Me gustaría mucho."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:791
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_44920c1f:

#   "My mother slipped out of her clothing and stood before me in her lingerie."
    "Mi madre se quitó la ropa y se puso delante de mí en lencería."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:792
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_973155bb:

#   c "Looking good, Mom."
    c "Te ves bien, mamá."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:794
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_07738dbb:

#   "My girlfriend slipped out of her clothing and stood before me in her lingerie."
    "Mi novia se quitó la ropa y se puso delante de mí en lencería."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:795
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_cc37d0a3:

#   c "Looking good, Nadya."
    c "Te ves bien, Nadya."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:797
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_fb7cc60e:

#   na "Thank you, sweetheart."
    na "Gracias, cariño."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:799
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_25942414:

#   na "Come here and give your mother a kiss."
    na "Ven aquí y dale un beso a tu madre."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:801
translate spanish ep023_nadya_talk_c2442eaa:

#   na "Come here and give me a kiss."
    na "Ven aquí y dame un beso."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:815
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_a221562c:

#   c "Hey Mom."
    c "Hola, mamá."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:817
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_06c4583b:

#   c "Hey Nadya."
    c "Hola Nadya."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:819
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_aabbda98:

#   c "Quite the bomb you dropped earlier."
    c "Menuda bomba has soltado antes."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:821
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_20334973:

#   na "I know, I’m so sorry."
    na "Lo sé, lo siento mucho."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:822
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_810d8bd6:

#   na "I wanted to tell you earlier in person, but you were just out of the medbay."
    na "Quería decírtelo antes en persona, pero acababas de salir de la enfermería."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:824
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_f0fc7517:

#   na "And then Lilly and Aven made their announcements..."
    na "Y entonces Lilly y Aven hicieron sus anuncios..."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:826
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_2f70b940:

#   na "And then Lilly made her announcement..."
    na "Y entonces Lilly hizo su anuncio..."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:828
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_c96ac942:

#   na "And then Aven made her announcement..."
    na "Y entonces Aven hizo su anuncio..."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:829
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_cf099f60:

#   c "You were worried I wouldn’t be able to take the shock?"
    c "¿Te preocupaba que no pudiera soportar el shock?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:831
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_610711a1:

#   na "Maybe...{w} Something like that."
    na "Tal vez...{w} Algo así."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:832
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_96f19fbc:

#   na "Maybe you’d be disappointed..."
    na "Tal vez te decepcionaría..."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:833
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_fc1d68d9:

#   c "Disappointed?"
    c "¿Decepcionado?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:835
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_d3d2a588:

#   c "I’m over the moon, Mom!"
    c "¡Estoy en la luna, mamá!"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:837
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_7e206ad0:

#   c "I’m over the moon!"
    c "Estoy encantada."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:838
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_46c0697a:

#   c "We talked it over, didn’t we?"
    c "Lo hablamos, ¿no?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:839
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_2724c85e:

#   c "We both decided we wanted this and I still do."
    c "Ambos decidimos que queríamos esto y yo sigo queriéndolo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:840
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_8acef7ce:

#   c "You don’t know how happy you’ve made me."
    c "No sabes lo feliz que me has hecho."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:842
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_93495d47:

#   na "Sorry, [p_name_short], I don’t know what came over me."
    na "Lo siento, [p_name_short], no sé lo que me pasó."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:843
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_4c8f87ca:

#   na "With all that happened on Petrarch and you being in a coma, I just started to panic."
    na "Con todo lo que pasó en Petrarca y tú en coma, me entró el pánico."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:845
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_8c85b57b:

#   na "What if you’d come out of that coma all changed."
    na "¿Y si hubieras salido del coma cambiado?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:846
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_6d199864:

#   na "We’d be all alone in the galaxy, running from the Sovereignty and my pregnancy would be a risk, a liability even."
    na "Estaríamos solos en la galaxia, huyendo del Soberano, y mi embarazo sería un riesgo, incluso un lastre."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:847
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_38163117:

#   c "I would never think something like that."
    c "Nunca pensaría algo así."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:849
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_dfd98ce4:

#   na "I know, and I’m sorry."
    na "Lo sé, y lo siento."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:850
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_478dc73f:

#   na "I just don’t want to lose you."
    na "No quiero perderte."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:851
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_f6ea7185:

#   c "You won’t and I won’t let anything happen to you and the baby."
    c "No lo harás y no dejaré que os pase nada a ti y al bebé."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:852
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_ff845d9d:

#   c "Shall we talk about happy things now, there’s been enough doom and gloom for one day, I’d say."
    c "Hablemos ahora de cosas felices, yo diría que ya ha habido suficiente pesimismo por hoy."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:854
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_d5a29f5b:

#   na "I agree."
    na "Estoy de acuerdo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:855
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_23d8719d:

#   c "How long have you known?"
    c "¿Desde cuándo lo sabes?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:856
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_b6f7749e:

#   na "A few weeks now."
    na "Desde hace unas semanas."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:857
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_1eb64a23:

#   na "I did a test when we were back on the Bastard, taking turns watching over you."
    na "Hice una prueba cuando estábamos de vuelta en el Bastardo, turnándonos para vigilarte."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:859
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_b8c800aa:

#   na "I was so happy at first, [p_name_short], becoming a mother again!"
    na "Estaba tan feliz al principio, [p_name_short] ¡volviendo a ser madre!"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:861
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_6352beed:

#   na "I was so happy at first, [p_name_short], becoming a mother!"
    na "Estaba tan feliz al principio, [p_name_short] ¡convertirme en madre!"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:863
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_caa59837:

#   na "Only after I told you the news at your bedside, did the worry set in."
    na "Sólo cuando te di la noticia junto a tu cama, empezó la preocupación."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:865
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_79d989db:

#   "I shushed her with a kiss, which she responded to greedily."
    "La hice callar con un beso, al que respondió con avidez."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:866
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_f526fd87:

#   "When we broke apart, there were tears in her eyes."
    "Cuando nos separamos, tenía lágrimas en los ojos."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:868
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_500c43d5:

#   na "Sorry for being such an emotional wreck right now."
    na "Siento ser un desastre emocional ahora mismo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:869
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_38260dd2:

#   na "I know hormones are a lame excuse."
    na "Sé que las hormonas son una excusa poco convincente."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:870
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_50699512:

#   c "Don’t worry, considering what we’ve been through, I don’t think you need an excuse."
    c "No te preocupes, teniendo en cuenta lo que hemos pasado, no creo que necesites una excusa."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:872
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_c6a860dd:

#   na "I’m so happy, [p_name_short]!"
    na "¡Estoy tan feliz, [p_name_short]!"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:875
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_318b9779:

#   na "All my daughters pregnant and I am too."
    na "Todas mis hijas están embarazadas y yo también."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:877
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_8616cd54:

#   na "Two of my daughters pregnant and I am too."
    na "Dos de mis hijas están embarazadas y yo también."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:879
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_3c449834:

#   na "One of my daughters pregnant and I am too."
    na "Una de mis hijas está embarazada y yo también."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:880
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_998cf4f9:

#   na "I can’t describe how special that feels."
    na "No puedo describir lo especial que se siente."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:881
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_02ff2f63:

#   c "There are going to be a lot of sleepless nights ahead."
    c "Nos esperan muchas noches sin dormir."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:882
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_7dadc7af:

#   na "True, but we’ll get through them together."
    na "Cierto, pero los superaremos juntos."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:884
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_7313b67b:

#   c "As am I."
    c "Como yo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:886
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_bb42872c:

#   "We retired to the bed, lying in each other’s arms."
    "Nos retiramos a la cama, abrazados."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:887
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_f3c6d380:

#   na "Do you need to go right now?"
    na "¿Necesitas irte ahora mismo?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:888
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_6b7cc1f3:

#   c "I can stay the night, if you want."
    c "Puedo quedarme esta noche, si quieres."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:890
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_05e595d7:

#   na "I would really like that."
    na "Me gustaría mucho."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:891
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_988bf987:

#   na "I’ve missed you so much."
    na "Te he echado mucho de menos."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:896
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_900d967f:

#   "We lay together in companionable silence, until the intercom crackled to announce that breakfast was ready."
    "Nos tumbamos juntos en un agradable silencio hasta que el interfono anunció que el desayuno estaba listo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:900
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_4a007b3a:

#   "As promised, I went by my mother’s quarters when it was time to go to bed."
    "Como había prometido, pasé por los aposentos de mi madre a la hora de acostarme."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:902
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_37b34beb:

#   "As promised, I went by Nadya’s quarters when it was time to go to bed."
    "Como había prometido, pasé por los aposentos de Nadya cuando llegó la hora de acostarse."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:907
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_c7e7b7d6:

#   "She was already dressed for the occasion."
    "Ya estaba vestida para la ocasión."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:909
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_973155bb:

#   c "Looking good, Mom."
    c "Te ves bien, mamá."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:911
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_cc37d0a3:

#   c "Looking good, Nadya."
    c "Te ves bien, Nadya."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:912
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_fb7cc60e:

#   na "Thank you, sweetheart."
    na "Gracias, cariño."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:914
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_25942414:

#   na "Come here and give your mother a kiss."
    na "Ven aquí y dale un beso a tu madre."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:916
translate spanish ep023_nadya_second_talk_c2442eaa:

#   na "Come here and give me a kiss."
    na "Ven aquí y dame un beso."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:927
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_711f53a2:

#   "Aven sprang up and ran toward me as soon as she saw me in the door opening."
    "Aven se levantó de un salto y corrió hacia mí en cuanto me vio en el hueco de la puerta."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:928
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_6e8629c6:

#   av "I’ve missed you so much!"
    av "¡Te he echado mucho de menos!"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:931
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_de439434:

#   "We kissed passionately, tears of joy streaming down my sister’s face."
    "Nos besamos apasionadamente, lágrimas de alegría corrían por el rostro de mi hermana."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:933
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_042676d0:

#   "We kissed passionately, tears of joy streaming down my girlfriend’s face."
    "Nos besamos apasionadamente y a mi novia se le saltaron las lágrimas de alegría."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:936
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_13bff363:

#   "Aven looked surprised when she saw me standing in the door opening."
    "Aven pareció sorprendida cuando me vio de pie en el hueco de la puerta."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:937
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_d6e91533:

#   av "There’s a sight for sore eyes!"
    av "Es un regalo para la vista."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:942
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_8b8bdd3a:

#   av "I didn’t know you were allowed out of bed."
    av "No sabía que podías salir de la cama."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:943
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_a1e06472:

#   c "I just left the medbay."
    c "Acabo de salir de la enfermería."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:944
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_d6b73542:

#   av "How are you feeling?"
    av "¿Cómo se encuentra?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:945
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_db5bb044:

#   c "I’m doing alright."
    c "Me va bien."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:946
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_5cb2f875:

#   c "You?"
    c "¿A ti?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:951
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_999f55b1:

#   av "I’ve been worried sick."
    av "He estado muy preocupada."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:953
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_105d1f0e:

#   av "And I’ve wanted to tell you something for weeks."
    av "Y he querido decirte algo durante semanas."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:954
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_870dda71:

#   av "I actually did, when you were still in a coma."
    av "De hecho lo hice, cuando aún estabas en coma."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:956
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_0176691f:

#   av "I’m pregnant, [p_name_short]!"
    av "¡Estoy embarazada, [p_name_short]!"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:957
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_86600e08:

#   av "We’re pregnant!"
    av "¡Estamos embarazados!"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:960
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_3d0c3a81:

#   "I lifted my sister off the ground and kissed her in response."
    "Levanté a mi hermana del suelo y la besé en respuesta."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:962
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_6288e8c0:

#   "I lifted my girlfriend off the ground and kissed her in response."
    "Levanté a mi novia del suelo y la besé en respuesta."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:963
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_dd5965c8:

#   c "That’s fantastic news!"
    c "¡Es una noticia fantástica!"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:965
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_13e598a8:

#   av "I know, right!"
    av "Lo sé."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:966
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_7a4ca2e7:

#   av "I was so worried I wouldn’t have been able to tell you."
    av "Estaba tan preocupada que no habría sido capaz de decírtelo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:967
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_c4e2cabe:

#   av "So I blubbered my confession next to your bed, hoping you would react in some way, but you didn’t."
    av "Así que lloriqueé mi confesión junto a tu cama, esperando que reaccionaras de algún modo, pero no lo hiciste."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:968
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_469cc3ac:

#   c "How inconsiderate of me."
    c "Qué desconsiderado por mi parte."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:970
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_ac792841:

#   av "Haha, yes, very!"
    av "Jaja, sí, ¡mucho!"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:971
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_cd4a2fa9:

#   av "But you’re here now!"
    av "¡Pero ya estás aquí!"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:973
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_07445ad5:

#   "We kissed again and stayed locked in an embrace for a very long time."
    "Nos besamos de nuevo y nos quedamos abrazados durante mucho tiempo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:976
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_3be17da6:

#   "My sister and I sat on the bed in silence for a while, holding hands."
    "Mi hermana y yo nos sentamos en la cama en silencio durante un rato, cogidas de la mano."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:978
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_328d6e76:

#   "My girlfriend and I sat on the bed in silence for a while, holding hands."
    "Mi novia y yo nos sentamos en la cama en silencio durante un rato, cogidos de la mano."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:979
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_52936d0d:

#   c "How far along are you?"
    c "¿De cuánto estás?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:981
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_fa20155e:

#   av "A few weeks, I guess."
    av "Unas semanas, supongo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:983
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_bdb0ebf7:

#   av "Certainly not as far as Eva."
    av "Ciertamente no tan lejos como Eva."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:985
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_1d8120a2:

#   av "I can’t wait to share the news with everyone."
    av "Estoy impaciente por compartir la noticia con todos."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:986
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_ac2bea30:

#   c "Me neither."
    c "Yo tampoco."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:987
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_195e0830:

#   av "If you’re not careful, the only thing I’ll want to do is cuddle and talk about how we’re going to convert my quarters into a nursery."
    av "Si no tienes cuidado, lo único que querré hacer es abrazarte y hablar de cómo vamos a convertir mis aposentos en una habitación infantil."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:988
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_7719db2b:

#   c "You have it all planned out?"
    c "¿Lo tienes todo planeado?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:989
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_4aac27d2:

#   av "Not yet."
    av "Todavía no."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:990
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_42f47372:

#   av "You’ll have a say in it as well, of course."
    av "Tú también podrás opinar, por supuesto."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:991
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_a6209eb9:

#   av "A small say, mind you."
    av "Un pequeño decir, eso sí."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:992
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_101e2ab8:

#   c "I feel very much included already."
    c "Ya me siento muy incluido."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:993
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_348ff93a:

#   av "I’m so glad you’re back!"
    av "Me alegro mucho de que hayas vuelto."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:995
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_1c7f6dbf:

#   av "We all have been."
    av "Todos lo hemos sido."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:997
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_63ab79d3:

#   av "I’m so glad you’re back."
    av "Me alegro mucho de que hayas vuelto."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:998
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_7313b67b:

#   c "As am I."
    c "Como yo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1000
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_72bbb168:

#   av "I still can’t believe you managed to save Eva."
    av "Todavía no puedo creer que te las arreglaste para salvar a Eva."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1001
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_bb604071:

#   av "I mean, I was there to see it with my own eyes."
    av "Estuve allí para verlo con mis propios ojos."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1003
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_a2c5f723:

#   av "If I didn’t know better, I’d say it was magic."
    av "Si no lo supiera, diría que es magia."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1004
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_925aff2d:

#   c "I can see why you might feel that way."
    c "Entiendo por qué te sientes así."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1005
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_8a3e63b0:

#   c "But I think there’s a scientific explanation for it...{w} Somewhere at least."
    c "Pero creo que hay una explicación científica para ello...{w} En algún sitio al menos."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1007
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_0fcfb35d:

#   av "I’m sure many scientists would love to poke around inside your brain."
    av "Seguro que a muchos científicos les encantaría hurgar en su cerebro."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1008
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_b0a9261f:

#   av "If it’s your brain that’s actually capable of what you did to Eva."
    av "Si es tu cerebro el que realmente es capaz de lo que le hiciste a Eva."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1009
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_bd3ed9cc:

#   c "I’m not sure where the power comes from, but my brain would be the best bet."
    c "No estoy seguro de dónde viene la energía, pero mi cerebro sería la mejor apuesta."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1010
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_7b55a8a6:

#   c "It’s like every sensation is heightened a thousand times."
    c "Es como si cada sensación se multiplicara por mil."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1011
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_29ff2abf:

#   c "When I’ve achieved a complete understanding of something, I’m able to manipulate the object or its surroundings."
    c "Cuando he alcanzado una comprensión completa de algo, soy capaz de manipular el objeto o su entorno."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1013
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_a57cc1e1:

#   c "With Eva, I just knew how to fix her and the baby."
    c "Con Eva, sólo sabía cómo arreglarla a ella y al bebé."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1015
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_485ca253:

#   c "With Eva, I just knew how to fix her."
    c "Con Eva, sólo sabía cómo arreglarla."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1016
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_cf3c81b4:

#   av "And it drained you completely in the process."
    av "Y te agotó por completo en el proceso."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1017
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_f55b01bc:

#   c "It did, yes."
    c "Lo hizo, sí."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1018
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_cd373f1b:

#   c "I guess something like that requires a lot of a person."
    c "Supongo que algo así requiere mucho de una persona."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1020
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_79a28456:

#   av "Yeah, I can only imagine."
    av "Sí, sólo puedo imaginarlo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1021
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_36490aad:

#   av "So smaller efforts shouldn’t send you into a coma?"
    av "¿Así que los esfuerzos menores no deberían dejarte en coma?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1022
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_8d5220cd:

#   c "That’s the theory."
    c "Esa es la teoría."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1023
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_e6207798:

#   c "I’m going to practice of course, it could be a very useful set of skills to have."
    c "Voy a practicar, por supuesto, podría ser un conjunto de habilidades muy útil tener."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1025
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_02d8419a:

#   av "I have no doubt."
    av "No lo dudo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1026
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_a5bbe44b:

#   av "You should try and use it as a weapon."
    av "Deberías intentar usarlo como arma."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1027
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_5c120def:

#   c "Yes, that’s an interesting thought, isn’t it?"
    c "Sí, es una idea interesante, ¿no?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1028
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_ce1c2e89:

#   av "I could set up some training scenarios for you."
    av "Podría preparar algunos escenarios de entrenamiento para ti."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1029
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_dac66d8e:

#   av "It might give us an edge if we ever found ourselves in hot water again."
    av "Podría darnos una ventaja si alguna vez nos encontramos en agua caliente de nuevo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1030
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_39854ac8:

#   c "Considering our history, that’s bound to happen sooner or later."
    c "Teniendo en cuenta nuestra historia, eso ocurrirá tarde o temprano."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1031
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_7e2f38ea:

#   av "Exactly."
    av "Exactamente."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1032
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_a9067051:

#   c "Do you know what happened with Agust after the procedure was completed?"
    c "¿Sabe qué pasó con Agust una vez finalizado el procedimiento?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1034
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_b2126cf2:

#   av "Vaguely, I was too distressed to care most of the time, I’m afraid."
    av "Vagamente, estaba demasiado angustiado para preocuparme la mayor parte del tiempo, me temo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1035
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_9a92a568:

#   av "The soldiers pulled Agust off the operating table and carried him out."
    av "Los soldados sacaron a Agust de la mesa de operaciones y se lo llevaron."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1036
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_5e2d24e1:

#   av "At first we were still under guard, like they were waiting for some senior officer to return or something, but nobody ever came."
    av "Al principio seguíamos bajo vigilancia, como si estuvieran esperando a que volviera algún oficial superior o algo así, pero nunca vino nadie."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1037
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_51d7354c:

#   av "The remaining soldiers all received a simultaneous radio broadcast and then they just marched out, leaving us behind."
    av "Todos los soldados restantes recibieron una transmisión de radio simultánea y luego se marcharon, dejándonos atrás."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1040
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_8ac9e001:

#   av "The same thing happened outside, according to Mom."
    av "Lo mismo ocurrió fuera, según mamá."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1042
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_534ae18e:

#   av "The same thing happened outside, according to Nadya."
    av "Lo mismo ocurrió fuera, según Nadya."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1043
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_ea9fc207:

#   c "Lilly thinks there was some medical emergency involving Agust."
    c "Lilly cree que hubo alguna emergencia médica que involucró a Agust."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1044
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_49aadff0:

#   av "Considering what happened with you, I think that’s a reasonable assumption."
    av "Considerando lo que pasó contigo, creo que es una suposición razonable."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1045
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_68080cba:

#   c "Likely the medical facilities on their flagship didn’t cut it, so they pulled out of Petrarch entirely."
    c "Probablemente las instalaciones médicas de su buque insignia no eran suficientes, así que se retiraron por completo de Petrarch."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1047
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_ffc14efb:

#   av "Yes, they must have, with the intention of returning at some point."
    av "Sí, deben haberlo hecho, con la intención de volver en algún momento."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1048
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_fcadd332:

#   c "Eva told me that Thyia took it upon herself to destroy the compounds left on Petrarch."
    c "Eva me dijo que Thyia se encargó de destruir los compuestos dejados en Petrarca."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1050
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_f7a0f280:

#   av "Yes, she did."
    av "Sí, lo hizo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1051
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_285f8bb9:

#   av "Luckily there weren’t that many structures on Petrarch, but it still took several weeks to lay waste to the lot of them."
    av "Por suerte, no había tantas estructuras en Petrarca, pero aun así tardamos varias semanas en arrasarlas."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1052
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_d64f2ef6:

#   c "So there’s no chance they’ll find anything?"
    c "¿Así que no hay posibilidad de que encuentren nada?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1054
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_b1cf6479:

#   av "There’s always a chance, but on Petrarch I think it’s unlikely they’ll find anything."
    av "Siempre hay una posibilidad, pero en Petrarca creo que es poco probable que encuentren algo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1055
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_9488250e:

#   av "Thyia was very thorough."
    av "Thyia fue muy minuciosa."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1056
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_b9aa15aa:

#   c "I’m happy to hear that."
    c "Me alegra oírlo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1057
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_e892027c:

#   av "Do you know what you want to do next?"
    av "¿Sabe qué quiere hacer a continuación?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1058
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_058dd7b5:

#   c "Yes, I think so."
    c "Sí, creo que sí."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1059
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_141e1d78:

#   c "I’ll update you all once I’m ready."
    c "Os pondré al día cuando esté listo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1062
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_595853b8:

#   c "First I want to enjoy some time with you and our baby."
    c "Primero quiero disfrutar de un tiempo contigo y con nuestro bebé."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1064
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_f6f453b8:

#   c "First I want to enjoy some time with you."
    c "Primero quiero disfrutar de un rato contigo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1066
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_a1be5d84:

#   av "I’d like that."
    av "Eso me gustaría."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1068
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_3bccbe3d:

#   "Aven and I fell back onto the bed and cuddled."
    "Aven y yo nos tumbamos en la cama y nos abrazamos."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1069
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_ac522ed9:

#   "We fell asleep not long after and woke up arm and arm."
    "Nos quedamos dormidos poco después y nos despertamos cogidos del brazo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1071
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_6daf25be:

#   "I kissed my sister goodbye and resumed wandering through the ship."
    "Me despedí de mi hermana con un beso y volví a pasear por la nave."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1073
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_b68adc4c:

#   "I kissed her goodbye and resumed wandering through the ship."
    "Le di un beso de despedida y volví a pasear por la nave."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1075
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_d74bb484:

#   av "Okay, let me know when you are."
    av "Bien, avísame cuando estés."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1076
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_255ecca1:

#   c "I will."
    c "Lo haré."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1078
translate spanish ep023_aven_talk_c8dfb4c4:

#   "I left Aven and resumed wandering through the ship."
    "Dejé a Aven y volví a vagar por la nave."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1091
translate spanish ep023_aven_second_talk_f4343d00:

#   "Aven and I had both asked our mother and sisters to come to my quarters."
    "Aven y yo habíamos pedido a nuestra madre y hermanas que vinieran a mis aposentos."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1093
translate spanish ep023_aven_second_talk_57047910:

#   "Aven and I had both asked Nadya, Eva and Aven to come to my quarters."
    "Aven y yo habíamos pedido a Nadya, Eva y Aven que vinieran a mis aposentos."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1094
translate spanish ep023_aven_second_talk_41f33976:

#   "They entered one by one."
    "Entraron de uno en uno."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1097
translate spanish ep023_aven_second_talk_62764e18:

#   e "I have a feeling what this is about."
    e "Presiento de qué se trata."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1099
translate spanish ep023_aven_second_talk_6b51495e:

#   l "Me too."
    l "A mí también."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1101
translate spanish ep023_aven_second_talk_3428fa16:

#   na "Shush girls, let Aven and [p_name] have their moment."
