# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1396
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_84c56714:

#   th "Yes, although he tried to talk me out of it, the first time I tried to shut him down."
    th "Sí, aunque intentó disuadirme, la primera vez intenté callarle."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1398
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_128d718e:

#   th "He began a long diatribe about the ethics of terminating synthetic life."
    th "Comenzó una larga diatriba sobre la ética de poner fin a la vida sintética."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1399
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_fd4a4e1d:

#   c "But you managed to convince him it was just something temporary?"
    c "¿Pero lograste convencerlo de que sólo era algo temporal?"

