translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_6f89eedc:

#   th "Yes, we did."
    th "Sí, lo hicimos."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1413
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_3351bc6c:

#   th "Petrarch appears to have been sparsely populated."
    th "Petrarca parece haber estado poco poblada."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1414
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_25a48138:

#   th "Once we knew where to look, the Bastard could only pick up a few signatures."
    th "Una vez que supimos dónde buscar, el Bastardo sólo pudo recoger unas pocas firmas."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1415
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_b26c168e:

#   th "So after scorching the interior of the temple and the compound we were staying, we moved onto the other locations."
    th "Así que después de abrasar el interior del templo y el recinto en el que nos alojábamos, pasamos a los demás lugares."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1416
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_ed1c176a:

#   th "The temple was the largest structure on the planet."
    th "El templo era la estructura más grande del planeta."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1417
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_245d59a5:

#   th "All the other buildings we found were comparable in size to the compound we used as a base of operations."
    th "Todos los demás edificios que encontramos eran comparables en tamaño al complejo que utilizamos como base de operaciones."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1418
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_e2c0b707:

#   th "It took us a few weeks to rig everything and after the detonations we visited each site to see if we got everything."
    th "Tardamos varias semanas en prepararlo todo y después de las detonaciones visitamos cada lugar para ver si lo habíamos conseguido todo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1419
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_9ec80cb9:

#   c "And did you?"
    c "¿Y lo hiciste?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1420
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_45ce10af:

#   th "Yes, we managed to destroy everything."
    th "Sí, conseguimos destruirlo todo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1421
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_e2cf7eed:

#   th "Jade has assured us that no amount of computer forensics will be able to salvage anything in there."
    th "Jade nos ha asegurado que ninguna cantidad de informática forense será capaz de salvar nada allí."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1422
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_1371a9cc:

#   th "So all the records have been wiped."
    th "Así que todos los registros han sido borrados."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1423
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_05cd1538:

#   c "Agust sure won’t be happy."
    c "Seguro que Agust no estará contento."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1425
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_d04b2ea7:

#   th "No, he probably already isn’t."
    th "No, probablemente ya no lo es."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1426
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_1a725ca0:

#   th "Céline left a few warning beacons when we pulled away from Petrarch."
    th "Céline dejó algunas balizas de advertencia cuando nos alejamos de Petrarch."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1427
translate spanish ep023_thyia_talk_9992cb78:

#   c "Has one of those beacons been triggered?"
    c "¿Se ha activado alguna de esas balizas?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1429
