#   c "I take it you’re glad that I’m back?"
    c "¿Supongo que te alegras de que haya vuelto?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1660
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_82b75a1c:

#   ce "Glad doesn’t even begin to describe it."
    ce "Alegre no es ni siquiera el comienzo para describirlo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1662
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_83472d89:

#   c "I hope you’re glad that I’m back?"
    c "Espero que estés contento de que haya vuelto."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1664
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_f617ee6b:

#   ce "Very much so."
    ce "Muchísimo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1667
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_27bd6c27:

#   j "Your mother told us you were out of the medbay, but I didn’t think you’d be walking around so soon."
    j "Tu madre nos dijo que habías salido de la enfermería, pero no creí que fueras a salir tan pronto."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1669
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_2d5daaba:

#   j "Nadya told us you were out of the medbay, but I didn’t think you’d be walking around so soon."
    j "Nadya nos dijo que habías salido de la enfermería, pero no pensé que andarías por ahí tan pronto."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1670
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_ac2bea30:

#   c "Me neither."
    c "Yo tampoco."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1671
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_62ba90cf:

#   j "Considering the feat you’ve pulled off, I was dreading you’d be in the medbay for months."
    j "Considerando la hazaña que has logrado, temía que estuvieras en la enfermería durante meses."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1672
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_7fbf7a1b:

#   j "Then again, you came out of your coma pretty quick."
    j "Por otra parte, saliste del coma bastante rápido."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1675
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_86be07ff:

#   j "I’m so happy you’re back!"
    j "Me alegro mucho de que hayas vuelto."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1676
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_f765b63f:

#   c "What were you girls working on?"
    c "¿En qué estabais trabajando?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1678
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_b3288799:

#   ce "We’ve just finalized the security checks for several software patches that Jade and I devised."
    ce "Acabamos de finalizar las comprobaciones de seguridad de varios parches de software que Jade y yo hemos ideado."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1680
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_27cacaa0:

#   j "The TGN Ypotryll was able to subvert all of our early-warning systems when they approached Petrarch."
    j "El TGN Ypotryll fue capaz de subvertir todos nuestros sistemas de alerta temprana cuando se acercaron a Petrarch."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1682
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_7de62d30:

#   ce "The orbital probes didn’t pick up any activity, so we looked into why that happened."
    ce "Las sondas orbitales no captaron ninguna actividad, así que investigamos por qué ocurrió eso."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1683
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_0d3cc6fd:

#   c "Did the battle cruiser use some sort of cloaking technique?"
    c "¿El crucero de batalla usó algún tipo de técnica de camuflaje?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1685
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_0f7028f9:

#   j "No, they didn’t."
    j "No, no lo hicieron."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1686
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_4108add7:

#   j "They managed to shut down those probes remotely."
    j "Consiguieron apagar esas sondas a distancia."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1687
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_98f1938e:

#   c "I thought those probes were secured?"
    c "Pensé que esas sondas estaban aseguradas."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1689
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_9111b89d:

#   ce "Yes, they’re supposedly top of the line, military grade."
    ce "Sí, se supone que son de primera línea, de grado militar."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1690
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_6ac07940:

#   ce "So we combed through everything and Jade eventually found out how they did it."
    ce "Así que revisamos todo y Jade acabó descubriendo cómo lo hacían."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1692
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_07e636a4:

#   j "Those probes had a software backdoor."
    j "Esas sondas tenían una puerta trasera de software."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1693
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_4b70257c:

#   j "Really cleverly designed, so it could only have been done during production."
    j "Muy bien diseñado, por lo que sólo podría haberse hecho durante la producción."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1694
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_e25e4dfb:

#   j "The company that produces them is a large manufacturer of all kinds of technology in one of the neutral systems."
    j "La empresa que los produce es un gran fabricante de todo tipo de tecnología en uno de los sistemas neutros."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1695
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_67c94922:

#   j "Digging deeper, I found out that the company in turn is owned by another larger conglomerate."
    j "Indagando más, descubrí que la empresa es a su vez propiedad de otro conglomerado mayor."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1697
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_8cb7e1ad:

#   j "That’s when the shell companies started appearing."
    j "Fue entonces cuando empezaron a aparecer las empresas fantasma."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1698
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_ea1fbfc0:

#   j "I’m not a hundred percent sure, but I think the factory that produces the probes is ultimately owned by the Sovereignty."
    j "No estoy seguro al cien por cien, pero creo que la fábrica que produce las sondas es, en última instancia, propiedad del Soberano."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1699
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_e61351f2:

#   c "And they’re the only ones with access to the backdoor?"
    c "¿Y son los únicos con acceso a la puerta trasera?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1700
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_e7bc106e:

#   j "Yes, I think so."
    j "Sí, creo que sí."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1702
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_1112a797:

#   ce "So we got a little paranoid and spent the past weeks going over every piece of hardware and software."
    ce "Así que nos pusimos un poco paranoicos y pasamos las últimas semanas revisando cada pieza de hardware y software."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1703
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_15d9106e:

#   c "How bad was it?"
    c "¿Qué tan malo fue?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1705
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_3ae3b932:

#   j "Not that bad, only minor stuff, apart from the comprimised probes."
    j "No tan mal, sólo cosas menores, aparte de las sondas comprimidas."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1706
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_5b3ca3c7:

#   j "I’ve hardened the security of every system on the ship and any smart weapons we have on board."
    j "He reforzado la seguridad de todos los sistemas de la nave y las armas inteligentes que tenemos a bordo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1708
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_c852f547:

#   ce "Yes, we went through everything with a fine-toothed comb."
    ce "Sí, lo hemos revisado todo con lupa."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1709
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_847fca40:

#   ce "So we’ll be better protected once the Sovereignty comes knocking."
    ce "Así estaremos mejor protegidos cuando la Soberanía llame a la puerta."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1710
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_0a2ff617:

#   c "It’s likely that they will, so good job you two."
    c "Es probable que lo hagan, así que buen trabajo a los dos."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1711
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_38694b92:

#   c "I’m planning on taking the fight to the Sovereignty, so being less vulnerable to their attacks is going to help for sure."
    c "Estoy planeando llevar la lucha al Soberano, así que ser menos vulnerable a sus ataques me va a ayudar seguro."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1712
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_7f1b7b37:

#   c "I’m going to discuss the plans in more detail soon, so I’ll let you know once I’m ready."
    c "Pronto hablaré de los planes con más detalle, así que os lo haré saber cuando esté listo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1714
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_e5a13291:

#   ce "Of course."
    ce "Por supuesto."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1716
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_46e89fb4:

#   j "If you need any technical input, we’re available."
    j "Si necesita información técnica, estamos a su disposición."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1718
translate spanish ep023_jade_celine_talk_cfbbbaf7:

#   "I left both women to work on finalizing their security review."
    "Dejé a ambas mujeres trabajando en la finalización de su revisión de seguridad."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1726
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_04ddf849:

#   "I’d hoped to find Raene inside her quarters, but she wasn’t there."
    "Esperaba encontrar a Raene en sus aposentos, pero no estaba."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1728
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_e1535e17:

#   "The door of Ziv’s quarters was ajar and I could hear voices inside."
    "La puerta de los aposentos de Ziv estaba entreabierta y podía oír voces dentro."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1730
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_1755ffec:

#   "After knocking, Ziv invited me in."
    "Después de llamar, Ziv me invitó a entrar."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1731
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_09f90eb8:

#   c "Ah, there you are."
    c "Ah, ahí estás."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1733
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_96d563f1:

#   ra "[p_name_short]!"
    ra "¡[p_name_short]!"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1735
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_e0dc1471:

#   "Both women got to their feet to embrace me, Raene got there first."
    "Ambas mujeres se pusieron de pie para abrazarme, Raene llegó primero."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1737
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_62fa1ff8:

#   "Raene got to her feet to embrace me."
    "Raene se puso en pie para abrazarme."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1738
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_fb8f7e1b:

#   ra "I’m so glad you’re okay."
    ra "Me alegro mucho de que estés bien."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1741
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_d00e5854:

#   zi "I missed you, [p_name]."
    zi "Te he echado de menos, [p_name]."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1742
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_e6c98684:

#   zi "Sorry I couldn’t visit you more, but I was part of Thyia’s sabotage efforts, so Raene went in my stead."
    zi "Siento no haber podido visitarte más, pero formaba parte de los esfuerzos de sabotaje de Thyia, así que Raene fue en mi lugar."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1743
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_48319372:

#   c "I don’t blame you one bit."
    c "No te culpo en absoluto."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1744
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_2e57cd1b:

#   c "I’m so happy to see you both again."
    c "Me alegro mucho de volver a veros."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1746
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_fdd3d580:

#   c "I’m so happy to see you again."
    c "Me alegro mucho de volver a verte."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1747
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_e1229664:

#   c "How have you been holding up?"
    c "¿Cómo lo llevas?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1749
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_d8069bf6:

#   ra "Reasonably well."
    ra "Razonablemente bien."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1750
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_6867b753:

#   ra "Everyone was so unhappy during your stay in the medbay."
    ra "Todo el mundo era tan infeliz durante su estancia en la enfermería."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1751
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_9349e470:

#   ra "Eva’s recovery brought a short moment of joy, but that soon ended when you didn’t seem to make any progress."
    ra "La recuperación de Eva supuso un breve momento de alegría, pero pronto se acabó cuando no parecisteis hacer ningún progreso."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1754
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_eb0700ab:

#   zi "The work on Petrarch kept us busy, but I could tell everyone was affected during the short moments of respite we had in the evenings."
    zi "El trabajo sobre Petrarca nos mantuvo ocupados, pero me di cuenta de que todo el mundo se sentía afectado durante los breves momentos de respiro que teníamos por las tardes."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1755
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_2536365d:

#   zi "Or maybe I’m projecting my own grief on everyone else."
    zi "O tal vez estoy proyectando mi propio dolor en todos los demás."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1757
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_f52d2748:

#   ra "No, I’m certain you’re not."
    ra "No, estoy seguro de que no."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1759
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_369c871d:

#   ra "You can’t imagine our relief when we heard you’d woken up."
    ra "No puedes imaginar nuestro alivio cuando supimos que te habías despertado."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1760
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_02d0449c:

#   ra "And you’re walking around the ship, so you must be feeling better?"
    ra "Y estás caminando por el barco, así que debes sentirte mejor."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1761
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_173b7d9d:

#   c "Yes, much."
    c "Sí, mucho."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1763
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_f583e47c:

#   c "I’m going back to my own quarters, Thim has released me from the medbay."
    c "Vuelvo a mis aposentos, Thim me ha liberado de la enfermería."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1765
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_a7b02eb1:

#   c "I’m going back to my own quarters, the autodoc cleared me."
    c "Vuelvo a mis aposentos, el autodoc me ha dado el visto bueno."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1768
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_53a169c5:

#   zi "That’s such good news."
    zi "Qué buena noticia."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1770
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_3cd6f2ed:

#   ra "Do you feel any different after what happened on Petrarch?"
    ra "¿Te sientes diferente después de lo que pasó en Petrarca?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1771
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_d44ef46a:

#   c "No, not when I do everyday stuff."
    c "No, no cuando hago cosas cotidianas."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1772
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_bc878a25:

#   c "When I concentrate though, I can tap into a reservoir of power I didn’t have before."
    c "Sin embargo, cuando me concentro, puedo aprovechar una reserva de poder que antes no tenía."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1774
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_4633b687:

#   zi "That’s fascinating."
    zi "Es fascinante."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1776
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_d3fe6d3a:

#   zi "Is that what you used to heal Eva?"
    zi "¿Eso es lo que usaste para curar a Eva?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1777
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_b184f765:

#   c "I did, yes."
    c "Lo hice, sí."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1779
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_28bf0320:

#   ra "But using that power is dangerous, clearly."
    ra "Pero usar ese poder es peligroso, claramente."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1780
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_f7fa1676:

#   c "It is if I do it without restraint, as I did with Eva."
    c "Lo es si lo hago sin freno, como hice con Eva."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1782
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_1b997159:

#   zi "You think this power can be trained?"
    zi "¿Crees que este poder se puede entrenar?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1783
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_4f7c2a96:

#   c "I think so, yes."
    c "Creo que sí."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1785
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_a5a5cb93:

#   zi "In that case, it’s a tool you can’t ignore."
    zi "En ese caso, es una herramienta que no puedes ignorar."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1786
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_d624d8a9:

#   c "A tool or a weapon."
    c "Una herramienta o un arma."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1787
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_d1b0f247:

#   c "In any case something I can’t ignore."
    c "En cualquier caso algo que no puedo ignorar."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1789
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_87443cf0:

#   "We were all silent for a while."
    "Todos permanecimos en silencio durante un rato."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1790
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_5a51c907:

#   "Raene was the first to break the silence."
    "Raene fue la primera en romper el silencio."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1792
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_4957be66:

#   ra "I forgot to ask why you were looking for me."
    ra "Olvidé preguntarte por qué me buscabas."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1793
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_1437962e:

#   c "I just wanted to see you."
    c "Sólo quería verte."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1794
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_fd292653:

#   c "You weren’t in your quarters so I went and looked and found you here."
    c "No estabas en tus aposentos, así que fui a mirar y te encontré aquí."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1796
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_eb4f2bc2:

#   ra "Oh...{w} I...{w} Uh...{w} I just want to talk to Ziv."
    ra "Oh...{w} Yo...{w} Uh...{w} Sólo quiero hablar con Ziv."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1797
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_ab828c75:

#   ra "Sorry, I’m making it worse by stammering."
    ra "Lo siento, lo empeoro tartamudeando."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1798
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_2f04a6c7:

#   ra "Now it sounds like we were-"
    ra "Ahora parece que estábamos..."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1799
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_62b1e80e:

#   ra "We were just talking."
    ra "Estábamos hablando."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1800
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_64719ec2:

#   c "I know, Raene."
    c "Lo sé, Raene."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1801
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_733ba312:

#   c "I have no reason to suspect otherwise."
    c "No tengo motivos para sospechar lo contrario."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1803
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_573ea058:

#   ra "Ziv has been such a great help in the past."
    ra "Ziv ha sido de gran ayuda en el pasado."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1804
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_1cc56d86:

#   ra "And she’s still helping me be myself."
    ra "Y sigue ayudándome a ser yo misma."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1806
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_d8b93f9d:

#   ra "Just like you are, [p_name_short]."
    ra "Igual que tú, [p_name_short]."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1808
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_ad45fcc2:

#   zi "Raene’s on her last round of injections."
    zi "Raene está en su última ronda de inyecciones."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1809
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_77501fa7:

#   zi "After that, her body should make the necessary hormones by itself."
    zi "Después, su cuerpo debería fabricar las hormonas necesarias por sí mismo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1811
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_f2e59d62:

#   zi "The balance has been restored, so to speak."
    zi "Se ha restablecido el equilibrio, por así decirlo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1814
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_24bcbaa7:

#   ra "So my breasts won’t get any larger, I’m afraid."
    ra "Así que mis pechos no aumentarán, me temo."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1815
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_b6139a0c:

#   c "You’re apologizing for your breasts?"
    c "¿Te disculpas por tus pechos?"

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1816
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_4cadd43d:

#   c "They’re perfect, Raene."
    c "Son perfectos, Raene."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1817
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_a440f854:

#   c "You’re perfect."
    c "Eres perfecta."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1819
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_98ebf960:

#   "Ziv smiled as Raene looked up at me shyly."
    "Ziv sonrió mientras Raene me miraba tímidamente."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1820
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_8c874213:

#   c "And I don’t think for one second you’d go behind my back, Raene."
    c "Y no creo ni por un segundo que lo hicieras a mis espaldas, Raene."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1822
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_5582558c:

#   ra "Thank you."
    ra "Gracias, señor."

# game/episode023_conversations.rpy:1824
translate spanish ep023_raene_talk_767b74e7:

#   ra "Sorry for making it all weird."
